## pgp

color body          color160        color1        "(BAD signature)"
color body          color37         color1        "(Good signature)"
color body          color1        color1        "^gpg: Good signature .*"
color body          color241        color1        "^gpg: "
color body          color241        color160        "^gpg: BAD signature from.*"
mono  body          bold                            "^gpg: Good signature"
mono  body          bold                            "^gpg: BAD signature from.*"

